snippet.textDisplay:
This is a kirtan from Haveli Sangeet and these guys are clearly spoiling it. Experimenting is good but stop always doing some stupid trendy fusions. Try doing it in a particular genre in which it sounds good and gives you the same vibe but with a different approach without stilling the beauty of actual kirtan.
Nowadays nobody is actually enjoying this stupid trend. We miss the beauty of music that we had.
Disappointed with Maithili Thakur even after knowing it is a cultural stuff like the way we had chaudhary, kesariya balam etc.and you presenting it in a very typical commercial way.
